[
  {
    "text": "Okay lets go through this one more time.",
    "start": 9.34,
    "duration": 2.08
  },
  {
    "text": "My name is Peter Parker.",
    "start": 11.44,
    "duration": 1.6
  },
  {
    "text": "I've had several Spider-Man movies...",
    "start": 13.04,
    "duration": 1.92
  },
  {
    "text": "and for the last 14 years I've had a few...",
    "start": 15.1,
    "duration": 2.28
  },
  {
    "text": "How It Should Have Endeds",
    "start": 17.38,
    "duration": 1.42
  },
  {
    "text": "I jumped out of the way of some grenades...",
    "start": 18.8,
    "duration": 1.62
  },
  {
    "text": "I argued with a talking lizard...",
    "start": 20.42,
    "duration": 1.76
  },
  {
    "text": "I decided to become an Avenger",
    "start": 22.18,
    "duration": 1.96
  },
  {
    "text": "I uh...",
    "start": 24.4,
    "duration": 0.82
  },
  {
    "text": "I even did this...",
    "start": 25.42,
    "duration": 1.46
  },
  {
    "text": "I will shoot this mortal man... in the face!",
    "start": 27.14,
    "duration": 2.88
  },
  {
    "text": "That one... that one got dark.",
    "start": 30.02,
    "duration": 1.46
  },
  {
    "text": "I'm not gonna lie.",
    "start": 31.48,
    "duration": 1.04
  },
  {
    "text": "But hey! At least I predicted the Marvel and Sony Deal!",
    "start": 32.52,
    "duration": 2.58
  },
  {
    "text": "So there's that!",
    "start": 35.1,
    "duration": 1.12
  },
  {
    "text": "Anyway.",
    "start": 36.34,
    "duration": 0.68
  },
  {
    "text": "For years I've always had a second chance...",
    "start": 37.02,
    "duration": 2.76
  },
  {
    "text": "at how it should have...",
    "start": 39.78,
    "duration": 1.04
  },
  {
    "text": "Spider-Man, would you stop narrating please?",
    "start": 40.82,
    "duration": 2.44
  },
  {
    "text": "What?",
    "start": 43.34,
    "duration": 0.6
  },
  {
    "text": "Wait. Are you that same kid from forever ago?",
    "start": 43.94,
    "duration": 2.7
  },
  {
    "text": "Yes.",
    "start": 46.66,
    "duration": 0.5
  },
  {
    "text": "Wow.  Now I feel old.",
    "start": 47.34,
    "duration": 1.68
  },
  {
    "text": "You were Narrating.",
    "start": 49.02,
    "duration": 0.98
  },
  {
    "text": "It's still kind of unnecessary.",
    "start": 50.0,
    "duration": 2.06
  },
  {
    "text": "But it's not!",
    "start": 52.06,
    "duration": 0.68
  },
  {
    "text": "Look, kid, it's kind of my thing.",
    "start": 52.74,
    "duration": 1.94
  },
  {
    "text": "I narrate.",
    "start": 54.84,
    "duration": 1.04
  },
  {
    "text": "I'm sorry. It's just what I..",
    "start": 56.06,
    "duration": 1.44
  },
  {
    "text": "No narrating!",
    "start": 57.68,
    "duration": 1.14
  },
  {
    "text": "Okay fine. Let's just see how Spider-Verse Should've Ended.",
    "start": 58.82,
    "duration": 2.72
  },
  {
    "text": "Mister Morales!",
    "start": 65.14,
    "duration": 1.12
  },
  {
    "text": "You're late again.",
    "start": 66.26,
    "duration": 0.96
  },
  {
    "text": "Einstein said time was relative right?",
    "start": 67.22,
    "duration": 1.66
  },
  {
    "text": "Maybe I'm not late.",
    "start": 69.06,
    "duration": 1.28
  },
  {
    "text": "Maybe you guys are just early.",
    "start": 70.34,
    "duration": 1.68
  },
  {
    "text": "Hehehe",
    "start": 73.78,
    "duration": 0.5
  },
  {
    "text": "I'm sorry.",
    "start": 75.02,
    "duration": 0.72
  },
  {
    "text": "It just was really quiet.",
    "start": 75.8,
    "duration": 1.68
  },
  {
    "text": "Wait a minute! You're not one of my students!",
    "start": 77.48,
    "duration": 1.8
  },
  {
    "text": "Who are you?!",
    "start": 79.32,
    "duration": 0.88
  },
  {
    "text": "Uh....",
    "start": 80.22,
    "duration": 0.5
  },
  {
    "text": "Whoa!",
    "start": 81.82,
    "duration": 0.5
  },
  {
    "text": "Swing up there, push the key, and blow it up.",
    "start": 84.28,
    "duration": 2.22
  },
  {
    "text": "There's not much time.",
    "start": 86.5,
    "duration": 1.52
  },
  {
    "text": "But I don't' know how to get up there.",
    "start": 88.02,
    "duration": 1.08
  },
  {
    "text": "Don't worry.  It's taken care of.",
    "start": 89.1,
    "duration": 1.58
  },
  {
    "text": "Here. Take this.",
    "start": 90.68,
    "duration": 1.02
  },
  {
    "text": "Oh!",
    "start": 94.62,
    "duration": 0.5
  },
  {
    "text": "All we have to do...",
    "start": 96.74,
    "duration": 1.28
  },
  {
    "text": "Is kill a couple of spiders...",
    "start": 98.02,
    "duration": 1.84
  },
  {
    "text": "and then we can bring your family back.",
    "start": 99.86,
    "duration": 1.62
  },
  {
    "text": "as many families as you want.",
    "start": 101.8,
    "duration": 1.92
  },
  {
    "text": "Tomorrow...",
    "start": 103.72,
    "duration": 0.76
  },
  {
    "text": "My collider.",
    "start": 105.1,
    "duration": 0.88
  },
  {
    "text": "Here's a bright idea...",
    "start": 105.98,
    "duration": 1.06
  },
  {
    "text": "Why don't you just do the thing now...",
    "start": 107.04,
    "duration": 2.06
  },
  {
    "text": "Instead of giving the good guys time to figure out a plan to stop you?",
    "start": 109.1,
    "duration": 2.5
  },
  {
    "text": "Good point.",
    "start": 112.26,
    "duration": 0.8
  },
  {
    "text": "Not tomorrow.  Let's do it now.",
    "start": 113.06,
    "duration": 1.38
  },
  {
    "text": "I'll see you at the Collider.",
    "start": 114.44,
    "duration": 1.42
  },
  {
    "text": "So I got my wife and kid back!",
    "start": 116.4,
    "duration": 1.84
  },
  {
    "text": "heheheehehe",
    "start": 118.46,
    "duration": 0.88
  },
  {
    "text": "Well they're not really your wife and kid.",
    "start": 119.34,
    "duration": 2.06
  },
  {
    "text": "You stole them",
    "start": 121.62,
    "duration": 0.96
  },
  {
    "text": "from a different dimension.",
    "start": 122.58,
    "duration": 1.3
  },
  {
    "text": "Yeah!  What if the other you gets super pissed",
    "start": 124.24,
    "duration": 1.84
  },
  {
    "text": "and vows revenge?",
    "start": 126.08,
    "duration": 1.12
  },
  {
    "text": "hehehe",
    "start": 127.84,
    "duration": 0.5
  },
  {
    "text": "That's not gonna happen.",
    "start": 128.34,
    "duration": 1.36
  },
  {
    "text": "You!",
    "start": 130.58,
    "duration": 0.5
  },
  {
    "text": "I'll kill you!\nAAAAAGH!",
    "start": 131.08,
    "duration": 1.3
  },
  {
    "text": "You know I have thermal vision right?",
    "start": 136.76,
    "duration": 2.14
  },
  {
    "text": "I can see you.",
    "start": 139.18,
    "duration": 1.18
  },
  {
    "text": "No you cant.",
    "start": 142.2,
    "duration": 0.8
  },
  {
    "text": "Uncle Aaron...",
    "start": 147.04,
    "duration": 1.04
  },
  {
    "text": "Please!",
    "start": 148.68,
    "duration": 0.56
  },
  {
    "text": "Prowler...What are you waiting for?",
    "start": 149.24,
    "duration": 2.12
  },
  {
    "text": "Finish it.",
    "start": 151.68,
    "duration": 0.72
  },
  {
    "text": "Spidey Sense!",
    "start": 154.1,
    "duration": 0.96
  },
  {
    "text": "Saved your life!",
    "start": 155.06,
    "duration": 0.92
  },
  {
    "text": "That's not nice!",
    "start": 156.6,
    "duration": 1.12
  },
  {
    "text": "You alright kid?",
    "start": 158.08,
    "duration": 1.12
  },
  {
    "text": "Whoa. Thanks Miles.",
    "start": 159.54,
    "duration": 1.36
  },
  {
    "text": "You saved my life.",
    "start": 161.02,
    "duration": 1.2
  },
  {
    "text": "You're welcome Uncle Aaron.",
    "start": 162.22,
    "duration": 1.26
  },
  {
    "text": "But you're still going to prison!",
    "start": 163.48,
    "duration": 1.84
  },
  {
    "text": "Awe Man!",
    "start": 165.68,
    "duration": 0.56
  },
  {
    "text": "You took my family!",
    "start": 167.72,
    "duration": 1.28
  },
  {
    "text": "Now I'm gonna make sure you never see yours again!",
    "start": 169.0,
    "duration": 3.12
  },
  {
    "text": "Kingpin Smash!",
    "start": 172.58,
    "duration": 1.6
  },
  {
    "text": "Get up Spider-Man.",
    "start": 175.5,
    "duration": 1.28
  },
  {
    "text": "You took my family!",
    "start": 185.48,
    "duration": 1.28
  },
  {
    "text": "Now I'm gonna make sure you never see yours agai...",
    "start": 186.76,
    "duration": 2.92
  },
  {
    "text": "Dad!",
    "start": 192.4,
    "duration": 0.5
  },
  {
    "text": "Miles?!",
    "start": 192.9,
    "duration": 0.56
  },
  {
    "text": "I mean uh... ehem.. uh...",
    "start": 193.5,
    "duration": 1.68
  },
  {
    "text": "Thank you for your bravery tonight!",
    "start": 195.18,
    "duration": 1.9
  },
  {
    "text": "Miles!",
    "start": 202.04,
    "duration": 0.5
  },
  {
    "text": "Miles!",
    "start": 202.9,
    "duration": 0.5
  },
  {
    "text": "Got a minute?",
    "start": 204.24,
    "duration": 0.88
  },
  {
    "text": "We forgot to do your cafe scene!",
    "start": 206.32,
    "duration": 1.64
  },
  {
    "text": "Cafe scene?",
    "start": 208.16,
    "duration": 0.98
  },
  {
    "text": "It's like a tradition!",
    "start": 209.14,
    "duration": 1.22
  },
  {
    "text": "Hey! Nice job, kid!",
    "start": 210.9,
    "duration": 1.28
  },
  {
    "text": "Is that Batman and Superman?",
    "start": 212.36,
    "duration": 1.92
  },
  {
    "text": "Yeah they just sit here all the time and pass judgement on peoples work...",
    "start": 214.28,
    "duration": 3.04
  },
  {
    "text": "It's kind of sad but it's all they've got...",
    "start": 217.32,
    "duration": 1.7
  },
  {
    "text": "so just go along with it.",
    "start": 219.02,
    "duration": 1.08
  },
  {
    "text": "Hey fellas!  Did you hear about how we saved the universe?!",
    "start": 220.1,
    "duration": 3.18
  },
  {
    "text": "Yes we did!",
    "start": 223.5,
    "duration": 0.86
  },
  {
    "text": "Congratulations!",
    "start": 224.36,
    "duration": 1.1
  },
  {
    "text": "I mean it's a miracle that you and your dad survived that explosion without a scratch...",
    "start": 225.46,
    "duration": 3.32
  },
  {
    "text": "but whatever!",
    "start": 228.78,
    "duration": 0.9
  },
  {
    "text": "I don't think that sounds weird.",
    "start": 229.68,
    "duration": 1.18
  },
  {
    "text": "Yeah sounds normal to me!",
    "start": 230.86,
    "duration": 1.54
  },
  {
    "text": "I survive explosions all the time!",
    "start": 232.4,
    "duration": 1.8
  },
  {
    "text": "Bruce what'd you think?",
    "start": 234.2,
    "duration": 0.98
  },
  {
    "text": "I don't know...",
    "start": 235.18,
    "duration": 0.68
  },
  {
    "text": "Felt like you copied a lot from the Bat universe if you asked me.",
    "start": 235.86,
    "duration": 2.8
  },
  {
    "text": "What?!  Copied!",
    "start": 238.82,
    "duration": 1.2
  },
  {
    "text": "How?",
    "start": 240.12,
    "duration": 0.5
  },
  {
    "text": "Uh.. Spider-Man's batcave!",
    "start": 240.62,
    "duration": 1.58
  },
  {
    "text": "Plenty of heroes have a secret lair!",
    "start": 242.2,
    "duration": 2.26
  },
  {
    "text": "Family member dies in an alley!",
    "start": 244.46,
    "duration": 1.34
  },
  {
    "text": "That's like standard hero motivation!",
    "start": 245.8,
    "duration": 2.18
  },
  {
    "text": "Noir guy!",
    "start": 248.24,
    "duration": 0.64
  },
  {
    "text": "You can't tell me he's not a batman knock off!",
    "start": 248.88,
    "duration": 1.98
  },
  {
    "text": "You're my favorite though by the way.",
    "start": 250.86,
    "duration": 1.96
  },
  {
    "text": "Thanks.",
    "start": 253.1,
    "duration": 0.74
  },
  {
    "text": "Pig man!",
    "start": 254.16,
    "duration": 0.68
  },
  {
    "text": "I don't know. You remind me kind of like Looney Tunes...",
    "start": 254.84,
    "duration": 2.2
  },
  {
    "text": "so... WB.",
    "start": 257.28,
    "duration": 0.82
  },
  {
    "text": "Close enough.",
    "start": 258.1,
    "duration": 0.88
  },
  {
    "text": "And I'm not sorry!",
    "start": 258.98,
    "duration": 1.16
  },
  {
    "text": "And you three.",
    "start": 260.18,
    "duration": 0.96
  },
  {
    "text": "Well I can't really think of anything yet",
    "start": 261.14,
    "duration": 1.28
  },
  {
    "text": "but I'll think of something.",
    "start": 262.42,
    "duration": 1.24
  },
  {
    "text": "Why is Batman so grumpy?",
    "start": 263.66,
    "duration": 1.6
  },
  {
    "text": "Is it because he's Batman?",
    "start": 265.26,
    "duration": 1.3
  },
  {
    "text": "Should I offer him some candy?",
    "start": 266.56,
    "duration": 1.22
  },
  {
    "text": "shh",
    "start": 267.78,
    "duration": 0.5
  },
  {
    "text": "I think you're just trying to find reasons to be negative.",
    "start": 268.28,
    "duration": 2.3
  },
  {
    "text": "No I'm not!",
    "start": 270.68,
    "duration": 0.72
  },
  {
    "text": "Yes you are!",
    "start": 271.44,
    "duration": 0.8
  },
  {
    "text": "Okay you got me. I am.",
    "start": 272.24,
    "duration": 1.2
  },
  {
    "text": "I don't mean any of it.",
    "start": 273.44,
    "duration": 1.3
  },
  {
    "text": "What do you mean?",
    "start": 274.74,
    "duration": 0.88
  },
  {
    "text": "Are you saying?",
    "start": 275.88,
    "duration": 1.04
  },
  {
    "text": "I'm saying I think you guys are the GOAT!",
    "start": 276.92,
    "duration": 1.54
  },
  {
    "text": "I don't think it's cool when he says that.",
    "start": 278.46,
    "duration": 1.8
  },
  {
    "text": "Greatest of all time!",
    "start": 280.26,
    "duration": 1.34
  },
  {
    "text": "That's high praise!",
    "start": 281.6,
    "duration": 0.84
  },
  {
    "text": "Wow! Really?",
    "start": 282.44,
    "duration": 0.76
  },
  {
    "text": "When Miles tells Peter...",
    "start": 283.2,
    "duration": 1.56
  },
  {
    "text": "You gotta go home, man.",
    "start": 284.76,
    "duration": 1.26
  },
  {
    "text": "And then sends him back to his universe",
    "start": 286.02,
    "duration": 1.8
  },
  {
    "text": "I'm just like...",
    "start": 287.82,
    "duration": 0.8
  },
  {
    "text": "He really is the best of all of us!",
    "start": 288.64,
    "duration": 2.16
  },
  {
    "text": "Wow! Batman really liked our movie!",
    "start": 290.8,
    "duration": 1.78
  },
  {
    "text": "It's so inspiring!",
    "start": 292.72,
    "duration": 1.28
  },
  {
    "text": "AAAAGHHH\nOkay let's turn it back a bit there, Batman",
    "start": 294.0,
    "duration": 2.78
  },
  {
    "text": "What's up Danger!",
    "start": 296.96,
    "duration": 1.2
  },
  {
    "text": "He's going through a lot right now.",
    "start": 298.16,
    "duration": 2.16
  },
  {
    "text": "He's kind of in a transitional period.",
    "start": 300.32,
    "duration": 2.46
  },
  {
    "text": "Ugh... I know those onions.",
    "start": 302.78,
    "duration": 1.46
  },
  {
    "text": "I swear you sound so familar.",
    "start": 304.24,
    "duration": 1.78
  },
  {
    "text": "*shrugs*",
    "start": 306.4,
    "duration": 0.64
  },
  {
    "text": "So is this gonna be like a thing now?",
    "start": 307.04,
    "duration": 1.34
  },
  {
    "text": "You guys keep teaming up with other spiders in the multi-verse?",
    "start": 308.38,
    "duration": 2.88
  },
  {
    "text": "Works for me!",
    "start": 311.26,
    "duration": 0.84
  },
  {
    "text": "I don't have any plans!",
    "start": 312.1,
    "duration": 1.04
  },
  {
    "text": "I mean I hope so!",
    "start": 313.34,
    "duration": 1.04
  },
  {
    "text": "We have to see where this is going.  Right?",
    "start": 314.38,
    "duration": 2.24
  },
  {
    "text": "What? Where what's going?",
    "start": 316.62,
    "duration": 1.16
  },
  {
    "text": "Hey.",
    "start": 319.12,
    "duration": 0.5
  },
  {
    "text": "Oh!",
    "start": 319.98,
    "duration": 0.5
  },
  {
    "text": "Hey.",
    "start": 321.98,
    "duration": 0.5
  },
  {
    "text": "Hey great job kid!",
    "start": 322.7,
    "duration": 1.2
  },
  {
    "text": "You didn't get your hand stuck in her hair this time!",
    "start": 323.9,
    "duration": 2.16
  },
  {
    "text": "What?",
    "start": 326.16,
    "duration": 0.5
  },
  {
    "text": "How do you guys know about that?",
    "start": 326.66,
    "duration": 1.08
  },
  {
    "text": "What do you mean how do I know that? Everybody knows",
    "start": 327.74,
    "duration": 1.88
  },
  {
    "text": "Thats why I like my hands extra slippery!",
    "start": 329.62,
    "duration": 1.02
  },
  {
    "text": "You're embarrassing me!\nWe're a big family!",
    "start": 330.64,
    "duration": 1.02
  },
  {
    "text": "Our boy's all growd's up.",
    "start": 331.66,
    "duration": 1.0
  },
  {
    "text": "Man... I wish I could hang out with all the Batmen in the Bat Universe.",
    "start": 332.66,
    "duration": 3.12
  },
  {
    "text": "Alright. Let me try and explain this to you.",
    "start": 335.78,
    "duration": 2.06
  },
  {
    "text": "This french fry is my universe.",
    "start": 337.84,
    "duration": 1.98
  },
  {
    "text": "It's awesome and perfect. It can do anything.",
    "start": 339.82,
    "duration": 2.36
  },
  {
    "text": "Your fries are different.",
    "start": 342.3,
    "duration": 1.76
  },
  {
    "text": "This one is vintage and retro.",
    "start": 344.06,
    "duration": 1.74
  },
  {
    "text": "kinda silly.",
    "start": 345.92,
    "duration": 0.88
  },
  {
    "text": "That's yours.",
    "start": 346.88,
    "duration": 0.96
  },
  {
    "text": "Your french fry is exactly what everybody wants its delicious.",
    "start": 347.84,
    "duration": 2.74
  },
  {
    "text": "And yours...",
    "start": 350.62,
    "duration": 0.88
  },
  {
    "text": "Your french fry has nipples.  It's weird.  It's gross.",
